Package main.model.tablemodel

Class AidList

java.lang.Object
main.model.tablemodel.AidList
public class AidList extends Object
AidList Class is TableView formats for DistributePage and DCHistoryPage. It contains information of aid list donated, requested by Donor and Ngo.
